  "title": "5 days Accounts Assistant (AP) up to $3000 (Novena)",
  "description": "<p>Accounts Assistant (Accounts Payable)</p><p>Salary: $2500 - $3000</p><p>Working Hours: Monday–Friday, 8:30am–6:15pm</p><p>Location: Novena</p><p>Benefits: 14 days Annual Leave, Performance Bonus</p><p></p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Process supplier invoices and staff claims accurately and on time</li><li>Match invoices with PO and DO and ensure proper approvals</li><li>Prepare payments via cheque, bank transfer, GIRO / FAST</li><li>Monitor payment schedules and reconcile vendor statements</li><li>Resolve invoice discrepancies and vendor payment issues</li><li>Maintain AP records, ledgers, and ageing reports</li><li>Support month-end closing, including accruals and reconciliations</li><li>Update cashflow records and assist in payment forecasting</li><li>Ensure proper documentation and audit compliance</li><li>Coordinate with internal departments on AP matters</li><li>Perform ad-hoc finance and administrative duties as required</li></ul><p></p><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>LCCI Accounting or equivalent qualification</li><li>Experience in Accounts Payable or accounting support preferred</li><li>Basic knowledge of accounting principles and GST</li><li>Detail-oriented with good organization and communication skills</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br />Company Name: Talent Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 24C2338</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Loke Sai Lye (Loke)</p><p>EA Personnel No: R24123366</p><p>Email: loke.dexter@talentrecruitmentsg.com</p><p>Contact Number: 8168 8648</p>",
